languages.text: "Даже преподобный этого не знал. Он опасался слежки, не желал выдать своего сына, если окажется под пыткой. Так что вам не добраться до нашего героя!"

traits.locale_text: "Даже преподобный того не ведал. Опасался слежки, не желал выдать сына своего ни словом, ни делом. Так что не добраться тебе до героя нашего!"

languages.text: "Even the confessor didn't know where it is. He was afraid of spies, or of giving his son's secrets away under torture. You see? You can't get to our champion!"

languages.text: «Ni siquiera el confesor sabía dónde está. Tenía miedo de posibles espías o de confesar los secretos de su hijo si lo torturaban. ¿Lo ve? ¡No puede llegar hasta nuestro campeón!».
languages.original_text: "Even the confessor didn't know where it is. He was afraid of spies, or of giving his son's secrets away under torture. You see? You can't get to our champion!"

traits.locale_text: «Ni siquiera el confesor sabía dónde está. Tenía miedo de posibles espías o de confesar los secretos de su hijo si lo torturaban. ¿Lo ve? ¡No puede llegar hasta nuestro campeón!».

languages.text: 「聴罪師でさえ、その場所を知らなかった。彼はスパイを恐れていたし、拷問で息子の秘密を漏らすことも恐れていた。分かるか？私たちのチャンピオンに近づけないのです！」
languages.original_text: "Even the confessor didn't know where it is. He was afraid of spies, or of giving his son's secrets away under torture. You see? You can't get to our champion!"

traits.locale_text: 「聴罪師でさえ、その場所を知らなかった。彼はスパイを恐れていたし、拷問で息子の秘密を漏らすことも恐れていた。分かるか？私たちのチャンピオンに近づけないのです！」

languages.text: “就连告解神父本人也不知道涅墨斯特在什么地方。他害怕身边有奸细，也害怕他自己会在严刑拷打之下泄露他儿子的下落。你看到了吗？你别想靠近我们的勇士！”
languages.original_text: "Even the confessor didn't know where it is. He was afraid of spies, or of giving his son's secrets away under torture. You see? You can't get to our champion!"

traits.locale_text: “就连告解神父本人也不知道涅墨斯特在什么地方。他害怕身边有奸细，也害怕他自己会在严刑拷打之下泄露他儿子的下落。你看到了吗？你别想靠近我们的勇士！”

languages.text: "Selbst der Konfessor wusste nicht, wo es ist. Er hatte Angst vor Spionen und davor, die Geheimnisse seines Sohnes unter Folter preiszugeben. Seht Ihr? Ihr kommt nicht zu unserem Champion!"
languages.original_text: "Even the confessor didn't know where it is. He was afraid of spies, or of giving his son's secrets away under torture. You see? You can't get to our champion!"

traits.locale_text: "Selbst der Konfessor wusste nicht, wo es ist. Er hatte Angst vor Spionen und davor, die Geheimnisse seines Sohnes unter Folter preiszugeben. Seht Ihr? Ihr kommt nicht zu unserem Champion!"

languages.text: « Même le confesseur ignorait où il se trouve. Il avait bien trop peur des espions ou de finir par révéler les secrets de son fils sous la torture. Vous voyez ? Vous ne trouverez jamais notre champion ! »
languages.original_text: "Even the confessor didn't know where it is. He was afraid of spies, or of giving his son's secrets away under torture. You see? You can't get to our champion!"

languages.text: "Yerini günah çıkarıcı bile bilmiyordu. Casuslardan ve işkence sonucu oğlunun sırlarını açık etmekten korkuyordu. Gördün mü? Müdafimize ulaşamazsın!"
languages.original_text: "Even the confessor didn't know where it is. He was afraid of spies, or of giving his son's secrets away under torture. You see? You can't get to our champion!"
